{"tid":1381200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為何IFC絕不能被打擾","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:04:55.000Z","uid":57424,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"187c84d397a3fbcc8d15efa714b4a05c5e2b11c5","tid":1381200,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=494087821402875&amp;id=406692330142425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D494087821402875%26id%3D406692330142425&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=59cccc46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=494087821402875&amp;id=406692330142425</a><br />\n<br />\n【為何IFC絕不能被打擾？】#從數據認識經濟<br />\n<br />\n昨日中、上環發生警民衝突，入夜後防暴警察更推進至IFC（國際金融中心）外天橋，一度欲進入商場，遭保安阻止並稱，「我哋唔歡迎你入嚟商場！ 」IFC立即獲得大量網民讚賞，表示會多多支持商場。<br />\n<br />\n到底，IFC被打擾一天會發生什麼事？<br />\n<br />\n這個甲級商場是由新鴻基地產、恆基兆業及中華煤氣三間公司合營，2005年9月全面落成。IFC由新地持有最多（佔50％），其次是恆基（佔40.77%），其他為中華煤氣持有。商場位於中環海傍的黃金商業土地，不少知名品牌進駐，包括連卡佛、Gucci、Chanel、Dior Beauty等名店，商鋪租金均是天價。商場上蓋更是保安森嚴的甲級商廈，不少中外大行總部也設於此，出入檢查嚴密，辦公室月租也貴絕中環。<br />\n<br />\n有多天價？翻查年報，IFC單2018年就可得51億元租金（港幣，下同），即每天就有1,400萬元租金進帳。真的是全香港最貴！（更可能是全球）如果再比較集團收入，會更易理解有多昂貴。以恒基的2018年收入為例，集團的整體租金收入為71億，其中IFC就佔了21億，佔比約三成！所以保安對防暴警察進入商場十分緊張，若有人擾亂商場秩序，騷擾到商戶及顧客，使租金下跌或不再續租，有誰負得起這個責任？<br />\n<br />\nSource：新鴻基年報、恒基兆業年報、煤氣年報<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; <br />\n<br />\n【搶先看，讓你更緊貼商業世界】：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/BusinessDigest.io/follow_menu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FBusinessDigest.io%2Ffollow_menu%2F&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=ca916d6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/BusinessDigest.io/follow_menu/</a> <br />\n<br />\n【立即追蹤Instagram，緊貼獨家IG Story】：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/business.digest.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbusiness.digest.io%2F&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=ebcf23fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/business.digest.io/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f908c38ec8bb842b7dd6d4de2534b1ac4c257b9f","tid":1381200,"uid":193565,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"明白了"},{"pid":"83faf7f81be3efac58bb9564ddb02d1ad61a2445","tid":1381200,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"所以唔關個發展商事<br />\n如果PP係做大陸水貨生意<br />\n咪又係比狗入"},{"pid":"e4b7e5bf4283bbd096321b417230911755afd621","tid":1381200,"uid":212843,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"大家知道邊到打無得輸啦?"},{"pid":"e3681866a17202fa64fc628ec929a1354f4cb470","tid":1381200,"uid":59489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:54:45.000Z","msg":"入到Ifc 可以直通金管局喎，緊係唔比你入去啦"},{"pid":"8c53a7ca1c536ecfdca62018fb27b472503fdc9b","tid":1381200,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}